{
  "id": "adv_main_02_12_05",
  "title": "東京編2章35話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "……と、いう訳で！\nさっそくインタビューしちゃいたいと思います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…S-so!\nI'd like to start the interview right away!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "まずはLizNoir、莉央ちゃんから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First up is LizNoir‚ Rio-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "……ねぇ、これはなんの茶番なのかしら？\n大体、貴方達レッスンはどうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ what's this charade about?\nWhat about your lesson?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんレッスンもするよ？\nでも同じくらい、これは大事なことなんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course we'll have our lesson?\nBut this is just as important!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.3866666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "私達はどんなアイドルになりたいのか、っていうのを\n改めてちゃんと、考えようと思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We wanted to take this opportunity to\nproperly think about what kind of idols we want to be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5533333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "そのためにも\nまずはみんなのアイドル像を聞いてみよう……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To do that‚\nwe thought we'd start by listening to everyone's image of an idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "そう……だからインタビューだったのね\nそれは分かったけど、あそこのカメラはなんのつもり？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… So that's why it's an interview.\nI understand that‚ but what's with the camera over there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルに、「アイドルとは？」を問う……\nその答えは、とても貴重……記録に、残すべき",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Asking an idol‚ \"What is an idol?\"…\nThe answer is very valuable… It should be recorded.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、私と怜ちゃんはADさん役なの\n書記が千紗ちゃんで、インタビュアーがさくらちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ Rei-chan and I are the assistant directors.\nChisa-chan is the secretary‚ and Sakura-chan is the interviewer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "完全にただの悪ノリじゃない、まったく……\nでも、力になれることがあるなら協力するわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is completely just you messing around…\nBut I'll cooperate if there's anything I can do to help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう！　じゃあお題はね……ばばん！\n「あなたにとって、アイドルってなんですか？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks! Okay‚ the question is… Ta-da!\n\"What is an idol to you?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_liz-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 79.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……その時間と場所でしか味わえない空間を\n作り上げて、ファンを幸せに出来る存在",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… an existence that can create a space that can only be experienced\nat that time and place‚ and make fans happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "そういう気持ちはもちろんある\n……けど私の根底にあるのは『戦い』、かしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I certainly feel that way too.\n…But at my core‚ it's 'battle'‚ I suppose.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルに成り立ての頃は麻奈を相手に\n麻奈が亡くなった後は彼女を超えるために",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I first became an idol‚ against Mana‚\nafter Mana passed away‚ to surpass her‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "そして今は、姫野さんの陰謀を阻止するために\n……まぁ最後のは、貴方達に託すことにはなったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and now‚ to stop Himeno-san's scheme‚\n…well‚ I ended up entrusting that last part to you‚ but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "自分の成したいことのために、戦いへ身を投じていく\nその生き様こそが、私にとってのアイドルよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "throwing myself into battle for what I want to achieve.\nThat way of life is what an idol is to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "莉央ちゃんらしくて、カッコいいね\n私には真似出来ないかもしれないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's so Rio-chan‚ it's cool.\nI might not be able to imitate that‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "さくらには似合わないわよ、こんなストロングスタイル\n貴方達らしい答えは、他に絶対あるはずよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This strong style doesn't suit you‚ Sakura.\nYou're sure to find your own answer that's right for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2533333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 138.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 138.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 138.5000000018
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "私、アイドルになって初めて知ったものが沢山あるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are so many things I learned for the first time after becoming an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 143.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "優やすみれに出会って、トリエルを結成して\n一緒に努力して、苦難を乗り越えてきた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I met Yu and Sumire‚ formed TRINITYAiLE‚\nworked hard together‚ and overcame hardships.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "二人と、そしてファンのみんなと\n喜びを分かち合ってきた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With Yu and Sumire‚ and with all the fans‚\nI’ve shared my joy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.92,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 157.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "そして、さくら達に出会って救われた……\n『絆』がこんなにも強いものだって、知らなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I was saved by meeting you‚ Sakura and the others…\nI didn't know 'bonds' were this strong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 166.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 168.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "私は、もう、みんなとの絆を断ち切りたくない\nそのためにも、アイドルで居続けるって決めたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want to break the bonds I have with everyone anymore.\nThat's why I decided to continue being an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 177.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "だから、さくら達の問いの答えは……\n『絆』なんだと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ the answer to your question‚ Sakura…\nI think it's 'bonds'.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 183.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_05-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……うん！　瑠依ちゃんらしいと思う！\nすみれちゃんは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Yeah! I think that's very Rui-chan!\nHow about you‚ Sumire-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
